headline: A Look at Regency Centers (REG) Valuation Following Upbeat Q3 Results, Dividend Hike, and Raised 2025 Guidance
summary: Regency Centers (REG) just posted its third-quarter results, showing year-over-year increases in both same-property Net Operating Income and Funds From Operations. The company also raised its 2025 guidance and announced a higher dividend. See our latest analysis for Regency Centers. Regency Centers’ upbeat quarter and increased dividend have caught investor attention, but the stock recently dipped, down 3.1% right after earnings, highlighting how positive momentum does not always translate...
